Compile & Run :
make

Game Description : 
This is simple game based on Opengl. You to have to avoid colliding with the obstacles in the path by moving left and right using LEFT & RIGHT ARROW KEYS. As the game progresses the speed with which the obstacles come increases. The instant you have a collision, your game is over.
Enjoy!

Remainder:
You might not see background mountain texture because of resolution issues. Mess with the code and make it visible for your resolution.
